  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 375f (190c).",
    "line a baking sheet with parchment paper. ",
    "in a large mixing bowl, whisk together egg whites and granulated sugar until stiff peaks form.",
    "add sifted flour, softened butter, room temperature egg yolks, vanilla extract, baking powder, and salt. ",
    "mix until a smooth batter forms. ",
    "transfer the batter to a piping bag fitted with a round tip.",
    "pipe into desired shapes onto the prepared baking sheet. ",
    "bake for 20 minutes or until golden brown. ",
    "allow to cool on the baking sheet for 5 minutes before transferring to a wire rack."
